address2: Room 706 No. 58, Dongzongbu Hutong Dongcheng District
longBusinessSummary: E-Commodities Holdings Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the processing and trading of coal and other products. It operates through two segments, Processing and Trading of Coal and Other Products, and Rendering of Integrated Supply Chain Services. The company also offers supply chain trading, logistics, and financing services; and constructs, manages, and operates processing factories and logistics parks; and renders warehousing, consigned processing, and logistics services. It operates in the People's Republic of China, South Korea, Indonesia, the Netherlands, Malaysia, India, Mongolia, Japan, Germany, and internationally. The company was formerly known as Winsway Enterprises Holdings Limited and changed its name to E-Commodities Holdings Limited in August 2016. E-Commodities Holdings Limited was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. E-Commodities Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Famous Speech Limited.
